author: @Alex4n3r
text: Interesting! The rules don't state that moving around costs halite. So when you do if ship.is_full: do dropoff it won't do it in the next turn but collect halite. So one needs another list of ship ids to care for their drop off. Also Direction.North is (0,-1), East is (1,0). The game isn't difficult but implementing small functions is a pain in the ass.
